Foot And Mouth Disease In Brazil
---------------------------------------
Follow-up report No. 3
See also:
21 Oct 2005 <http://www.oie.int/eng/info/hebdo/AIS_48.HTM#Sec2>
14 Oct 2005 <http://www.oie.int/eng/info/hebdo/AIS_49.HTM#Sec7>
